<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {

            .container {
                padding: 15px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Thank You for Choosing Us!</h1>
        <p>We sincerely appreciate your trust in us and hope you had a wonderful stay. Your satisfaction is our top
            priority, and we look forward to welcoming you back soon.</p>
        <a href="/guestadminpanel">View All Booked Hotels By You</a>
    </div>
</body>

</html>